<br />
<i>&lt;a id="anchorname"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</i><br />
<br />
Then you would make the HREF look like this:<br />
<br />
<i>&lt;a href="#anchorname"&gt;Anchor name&lt;/a&gt;</i><br />
